{"tid":612344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖）大學生搞ig黎呃錢 （2）","createTime":"2018-03-31T18:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T12:31:44.000Z","uid":110453,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"77daa0b98473428c6488864cf84509ef2b2a165c","tid":612344,"uid":110453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:31:45.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n話說我上次po左張報案卡之後，佢個晚就即刻打黎，希望我消案:-<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全無視左個陣係訓教時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都由佢，雖則我覺得佢冇乜悔意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我都放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咁二都凡事留一線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我有個條件就係要佢比個交代同寄返哂啲貨比佢所有嘅顧客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家已經過左10日問題係我想知有冇人仲未收到佢回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇收到可以立即帶同你嘅入數紙同埋對話內容報警處理。可能有人覺得我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我係唔想再有受害者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識人當差歡迎查詢，亦歡迎插我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/023129_20f902af88e13aa56c08e7139d805532.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F023129_20f902af88e13aa56c08e7139d805532.png&h=f6278573&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54e780e2c3a8b0ef4b645d3e371a30f6fa5d82ac","tid":612344,"uid":110453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"(有圖)大學生搞ig嚟呃錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/599805/page/17?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/599805/page/17?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"